COLLEGE 

For bonafide students with a General Weighted Average (GWA) of not lower than 1.20 and 1.30 and must: 

• Be enrolled in full load of academic units as prescribed in the curriculum; 
 • Have no grade lower than 2.0 for full scholar and 2.5 for partial scholar in any academic and/or non-academic courses; 
 • Have no “dropped” remark in any course previously enrolled
